    "description": "泰拉利亚大地在黑暗之神希洛斯的阴影下颤抖。请回应泰拉利亚永恒的守护者审判者的召唤，响应召唤并阻止希洛斯！<br><br>进入拥有8种精彩游戏模式和海量个性化角色的回合制角色扮演游戏。沉浸在故事带动的战役关卡之中，在PvP竞争中与来自全球的玩家角逐，并随着我们马不停蹄的更新步伐接受持续不断的新挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/509035cac2c3ecb494e2ba4633665cef.avif?t=1771951870\" width=624 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要游戏特色</strong> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>召唤800余名斗士</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/9a4bd89b65465fe585b6d51c8c4af120.poster.avif?t=1771951870\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/9a4bd89b65465fe585b6d51c8c4af120.webm?t=1771951870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/9a4bd89b65465fe585b6d51c8c4af120.mp4?t=1771951870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>收集来自15个阵营，数以百计的独特斗士，并将他们组合成击败你敌人的势不可挡的队伍。暗黑精灵，欧格林，战阀，蜥蜴人以及更多等待加入你队伍的斗士已整装待发，准备在你的带领下走向成功。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>掌握策略性的回合制玩法</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/bfbdfb7b98823d6efacdd54f8e639a03.poster.avif?t=1771951870\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/bfbdfb7b98823d6efacdd54f8e639a03.webm?t=1771951870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/bfbdfb7b98823d6efacdd54f8e639a03.mp4?t=1771951870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>为你的斗士换上你斩获的史诗级装备并为他们选择合适的天赋，打造无限的组合可能。升级你的队伍并以你的方式出击，施放强大的伤害输出技能和改变战局的辅助技艺。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在3种PvP模式中证明自己</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/96444992d865e510b061e65170ddc057.poster.avif?t=1771951870\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/96444992d865e510b061e65170ddc057.webm?t=1771951870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/96444992d865e510b061e65170ddc057.mp4?t=1771951870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>进入竞技场，和其他玩家对战，以解锁特殊的装备并在排行榜上获得好名次。然后，去在线竞技场的实时PvP战斗中展现你真正的实力。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索引人入胜的PvE内容</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/6be44d764b1e63229a7a4d31147c5c68.poster.avif?t=1771951870\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/6be44d764b1e63229a7a4d31147c5c68.webm?t=1771951870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/6be44d764b1e63229a7a4d31147c5c68.mp4?t=1771951870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在激动人心的暗黑魔幻故事配音下，从炫目的关卡中杀出一条血路。征服黑暗势力以及13名富有挑战的副本首领，挑战快节奏的阵营之战以及恶名昭著的末日之塔，赢得珍贵的战利品。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与好友组队</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/142fb7e00dca01d510bcb58c0c829628.poster.avif?t=1771951870\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/142fb7e00dca01d510bcb58c0c829628.webm?t=1771951870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/142fb7e00dca01d510bcb58c0c829628.mp4?t=1771951870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>和你的玩家伙伴携手挑战公会首领，赢得独特的装备，召唤新斗士的碎片以及更多惊喜奖励。当你所在的公会足够强大时，将可以参加史诗级的六头蛇冲突锦标赛，并与4支敌对公会队伍一较高下。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>流连于斗士的传说故事之中</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/acc952ae462044597867a5b352dd5526.poster.avif?t=1771951870\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/acc952ae462044597867a5b352dd5526.webm?t=1771951870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333480/extras/acc952ae462044597867a5b352dd5526.mp4?t=1771951870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>从独一无二的背景故事里了解泰拉利亚的居民以及这块神奇的大地。去YouTube上观看系列限定剧 《RAID: Call of the Arbiter》，更进一步沉浸在这个魔幻的世界里。",
